Source: breakpad
Version: 2024.02.16
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/google/breakpad.git
Upstream-Ref: v2024.02.16
Build-Depends: build-essential, autoconf, automake, libtool, pkg-config, zlib1g-dev

Package: breakpad
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Google Breakpad crash reporting system - runtime
 Breakpad is a set of client and server components which implement a
 crash-reporting system. The client libraries can be embedded in
 applications to capture crash dumps when they crash, and the server
 components process those crash dumps to produce stack traces and other
 debugging information.
 .
 This package contains the runtime libraries and tools.

Package: libbreakpad-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: breakpad (= ${version})
Description: Google Breakpad crash reporting system - development files
 Breakpad is a set of client and server components which implement a
 crash-reporting system. The client libraries can be embedded in
 applications to capture crash dumps when they crash.
 .
 This package contains the development headers, static libraries, and
 pkg-config files needed to build applications using Breakpad.
